---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy — Equipment Management International">
  <Nav />
  <main class="pt-20">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="bg-emi-charcoal text-white py-16 sm:py-20 scroll-mt-20">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold uppercase tracking-wide">
          Privacy Policy
        </h1>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mt-2">Effective Date: November 13, 2023</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Content -->
    <section class="py-16 sm:py-24 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none space-y-8 text-gray-700">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Introduction</h2>
            <p>
              Equipment Management International P/L is committed to protecting the personal information collected through our website. We follow the Australian Privacy Principles (APPs) in the handling of all personal information.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">APP 1 — Website Usage Data</h2>
            <p>
              Our site automatically gathers statistics including server addresses, domain names, accessed pages, referral sources, and browser types. We do not attempt to identify you or your browsing activities.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">APP 3 — Form-Based Collection</h2>
            <p>
              Personal data is collected only through feedback forms for service provision. We will only collect information directly from you and will provide explanations on forms about data usage purposes.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">APP 6 — Use & Disclosure</h2>
            <p>
              Email addresses are recorded only when you contact us and are used solely for that stated purpose. Please note there are inherent risks in online transmission of information.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">APP 10 — Data Quality</h2>
            <p>
              Information remains accurate and current, used only for intended purposes unless you've subscribed or joined as a member.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">APP 11 — Security</h2>
            <p>
              We use encryption and security certificates to protect your information. We permanently de-identify information after service completion, retaining only activity records.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">APP 12 — Access Rights</h2>
            <p>
              Upon request, you can view the information we hold about you and request alterations to ensure accuracy.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Additional Protections</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
              <li>Sensitive information collection requires explicit consent</li>
              <li>No overseas transfers occur without consent</li>
              <li>Government identifiers aren't used unless acting as government agents</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="border-t border-gray-200 pt-8">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Contact</h2>
            <p>
              If you have any complaints or queries regarding our privacy practices, please <a href="/contact" class="text-emi-gold hover:underline">contact us</a>.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
